---
import { FontAwesomeIcon } from "@fortawesome/react-fontawesome";
import { Github, Linkedin, Instagram } from "lucide-react";
import "./Header.css";
---

<div class="mb-10 mt-16 w-[80%]">
    <div
        class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-repeat-x animate-slide opacity-60"
        style={{
            backgroundImage: "url('img/pattern.png')",
            backgroundSize: "cover",
            zIndex: "-1",
            WebkitMaskImage:
                "linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0,0,0,1), rgba(0,0,0,0))",
        }}
    >
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
        <div class="relative inline-block">
            <div
                class="w-48 h-48 mx-auto rounded-full overflow-hidden border-4 border-[#ebeb33]/30 shadow-2xl animate-pulse-glow"
            >
                <img
                    src="img/yo.jpg"
                    alt=""
                    class="rounded-full w-full h-full object-cover"
                />
            </div>
            {/* Decorative ring */}
            <div
                class="absolute inset-0 rounded-full border-2 border-[#ebeb33]/20 animate-ping"
                style={{ animationDuration: "3s" }}
            >
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="name m-5 text-center">
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold">Daniel Plasencia</h1>
            <h2
                class="text-[#ebeb33] text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-gradient"
            >
                Ing. de Software con IA
            </h2>
            <div
                class="flex flex-row justify-center gap-6 items-center mt-8 mx-4"
            >
                <a
                    class="p-4 rounded-full bg-[#282c34] hover:bg-[#ebeb33] hover:text-[#16181d] transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-110"
                    href=""
                >
                    <Instagram className="w-6 h-6" />
                </a>
                <a
                    class="p-4 rounded-full bg-[#282c34] hover:bg-[#ebeb33] hover:text-[#16181d] transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-110"
                    href=""
                >
                    <Linkedin className="w-6 h-6" />
                </a>
                <a
                    class="p-3 rounded-full bg-[#282c34] hover:bg-[#ebeb33] hover:text-[#16181d] transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-110"
                    href=""
                >
                    <Github className="w-6 h-6" />
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="text-center w-full mt-12">
        <h1
            class="text-[#a6a6a6] text-lg md:text-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed"
        >
            Creo experiencias digitales perfectas, atractivas y accesibles,
            fusionando diseño y tecnología para resolver problemas de manera
            innovadora y eficiente, siempre poniendo al usuario en el centro de
            cada solución
        </h1>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-row w-full items-center justify-center mt-14">
        <div class="Imagen TRex mr-7 animate-bounce">
            <img src="img/trex.png" width="180" height="180" alt="" />
        </div>
        <div class="ml-7">
            <h1 class="font-bold text-2xl">
                "Te pierdes lo bueno buscando el error"
            </h1>
            <h2 class="text-[#DAD91A] text-xl text-center font-semibold">
                Kase. O
            </h2>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<style>
    @keyframes pulse-glow {
        0%,
        100% {
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(235, 235, 51, 0.4);
        }
        50% {
            box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(235, 235, 51, 0.8);
        }
    }
</style>
